description: Updates the EvaluationName of an Evaluation. You can use the GetEvaluation operation to view the contents of the updated data element.

parameters.name: EvaluationId
parameters.description: The ID assigned to the Evaluation during creation.

parameters.name: EvaluationName
parameters.description: A new user-supplied name or description of the Evaluation that will replace the current content.

nested_items.name: EvaluationId
nested_items.description: The ID assigned to the Evaluation during creation. This value should be identical to the value of the Evaluation in the request.
